Use shortcuts to move your selected tab. Also supports moving multiple selected tabs at once.
Lightweight extension with no gui at all.
Here are the preferred key bindings:

Move active tabs to left
alt + shift + left

Move active tabs to right
alt + shift + right

Move active tabs to left end
alt + shift + page up

Move active tabs to right end
alt + shift + page down
